<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Asset Allocation Notification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h2 {
            color: #333;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #555;
        }
        .asset-info {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #888;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Asset Allocation Notification</h2>
        <p>Dear <strong>Employeee</strong></p>
        <p>We have assigned you a new asset.</p>

        

        <p>If you have any questions, please contact the IT department.</p>

        <p class="footer">Best Regards,<br>Admin Team</p>
    </div>
